      <description>Children love mystery and make believe. As such, it&amp;#8217;s a great idea to incorporate some mystery party activities into the parties you are about to plan. Not only will these activities be fun to play, but they also perform an educational role in enhancing children&amp;#8217;s reasoning and analytical abilities. Plus they&amp;#8217;re really fun to create! [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-activities/"&gt;Mystery Party Activities&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Mystery_Party_Activities.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Children love mystery and make believe. As such, it&#8217;s a great idea to incorporate some mystery party activities into the parties you are about to plan.</p>
<p><a title="Venetian masks" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/76994867@N00/4079782102/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0pt none;" title="mystery party activities" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2631/4079782102_5775355d58_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Venetian masks" width="159" height="240" /></a>Not only will these activities be fun to play, but they also perform an educational role in enhancing children&#8217;s reasoning and analytical abilities. Plus they&#8217;re really fun to create!</p>
<p>The most obvious of the mystery party activities is to have a mystery party &#8211; where everyone comes in character and has to solve a mystery.</p>
<p>Obviously, if you have younger children attending, you may want to steer clear of the murder mystery theme. There are many packages available online which offer excellent mystery planning kits. Check them out!</p>
