      <description>Children love excitement and adventure. One way to guarantee they&amp;#8217;ll enjoy any party you throw is to make it a theme party. My daughters love birthday theme parties; whether their own or the ones of their friends. Putting together a theme party can be difficult. You&amp;#8217;ll need to do some brainstorming of what your little [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/birthday-theme-parties/"&gt;Birthday Theme Parties&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Birthday_Theme_Parties.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Children love excitement and adventure. One way to guarantee they&#8217;ll enjoy any party you throw is to make it a theme party. My daughters love birthday theme parties; whether their own or the ones of their friends.</p>
<p><a title="Smiling in Bubbles_2433c" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/62126383@N00/4066299323/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0pt none; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;" title="birthday theme parties" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2748/4066299323_1a889955e5_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Smiling in Bubbles_2433c" width="162" height="240" /></a>Putting together a theme party can be difficult. You&#8217;ll need to do some brainstorming of what your little girl loves to do (and characters she loves) to get an idea of what sort of theme is appropriate. You&#8217;ll then need to vary the rules of party games to ensure they suit the theme.</p>
<p>Take any of the many <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com" target=" " title="party games for girls">party games for girls</a> in this site and think about how the rules could be altered to match the theme. Get everyone to come in costume and make sure the party food also reflects the theme.</p>
<p>Just remember: any effort you invest in the planning will come back to you many times over both during and after the party!</p>
<p><small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="../wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="hoyasmeg" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/62126383@N00/4066299323/" target="_blank">hoyasmeg</a></small></p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/birthday-theme-parties/">Birthday Theme Parties</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/birthday-theme-parties/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
