      <title>Indoor Party Games For Girls</title>
      <link>http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/indoor-party-games-for-girls/</link>
      <comments>http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/indoor-party-games-for-girls/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Nov 2009 17:09:02 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Party Games For Girls</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Indoor Party Games]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[indoor party games for girls]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/?p=153</guid>
      <description>Every party where girls are guests will require some indoor party games to keep them entertained. There is a vast selection of indoor party games for girls from which to choose. This site contains lots of examples! However, a really cool game is to play &amp;#8216;Spin The Nail Polish&amp;#8217;. photo credit: Etsy KetsySit the girls [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/indoor-party-games-for-girls/"&gt;Indoor Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Indoor_Party_Games_For_Girls.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Every party where girls are guests will require some <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/indoor-party-games" target=" " title="indoor party games">indoor party games</a> to keep them entertained.<br />
There is a vast selection of indoor <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com" target=" " title="party games for girls">party games for girls</a> from which to choose. This site contains lots of examples! However, a really cool game is to play &#8216;Spin The Nail Polish&#8217;.<br />
<span style="float:left;"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/87457515@N00/3906123220/" title="Five on one swatch!" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2602/3906123220_bcb7f4f2a8_m.jpg" alt="Five on one swatch!" border="0" /></a><br /><small><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" title="Attribution-ShareAlike License" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" alt="Creative Commons License" border="0" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/87457515@N00/3906123220/" title="Etsy Ketsy" target="_blank">Etsy Ketsy</a></small></span>Sit the girls in a circle and have one nail polish in the middle. Taking it in turns, each girl spins the nail polish. The person to whom the top of the polish points has to paint one of the spinner&#8217;s nails using a nail polish other than the one used to spin (get hold of a range of non-toxic, multi-colored polishes to play this game).<br />
The game continues until all of the girls&#8217; nails are covered in polish! Lots of multi-colored fun!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/indoor-party-games-for-girls/">Indoor Party Games For Girls</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
