      <description>If the party you&amp;#8217;re planning for your daughter has lots of people coming, you&amp;#8217;ll need some party games for a large group. The most obvious solution is to have some tag-type games to ensure everyone is involved. It&amp;#8217;s good to combine games that everyone can play at once together, but also have some games available [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/group-party-games/party-games-large-group/"&gt;Party Games For A Large Group&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Party_Games_For_A_Large_Group.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>If the party you&#8217;re planning for your daughter has lots of people coming, you&#8217;ll need some party games for a large group.<br />
The most obvious solution is to have some tag-type games to ensure everyone is involved. It&#8217;s good to combine games that everyone can play at once together, but also have some games available for those who may not necessarily like running around.<br />
<span style=float:right;><a title="Multiple fun!!!!" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/32848143@N06/3874118153/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2511/3874118153_387e117b47_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Multiple fun!!!!" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution-ShareAlike License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Bluenose Canoehead" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/32848143@N06/3874118153/" target="_blank">Bluenose Canoehead</a></small></span>You could mix the games up, including some tag or scavenger hunt games, along with some more sedate pass the parcel games.<br />
The key point is to ensure that everyone is involved in something; you should keep an eye out for anyone who does not look engaged and get them to suggest some games that they would like to play.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/group-party-games/party-games-large-group/">Party Games For A Large Group</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
