      <description>Ok, so not everyone loves clowns. Over the years, they&amp;#8217;ve gained a bit of a bad rep, but whether you like or loathe them, it can be fun to have a clown birthday party. photo credit: Ed YourdonIf you love clowns, they&amp;#8217;re great to provide a bit of brightness and laughter. If, however, you&amp;#8217;re not [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/clown-birthday-party/"&gt;Clown Birthday Party&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Clown_Birthday_Party.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Ok, so not everyone loves clowns. Over the years, they&#8217;ve gained a bit of a bad rep, but whether you like or loathe them, it can be fun to have a clown birthday party.<br />
<span style=float:left;><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/72098626@N00/4016774316/" title="Yet another street fair, Oct 2009 - 69" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2512/4016774316_7df5f5a431_m.jpg" alt="Yet another street fair, Oct 2009 - 69" border="0" /></a><br /><small><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" title="Attribution-ShareAlike License" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" alt="Creative Commons License" border="0" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/72098626@N00/4016774316/" title="Ed Yourdon" target="_blank">Ed Yourdon</a></small></span>If you love clowns, they&#8217;re great to provide a bit of brightness and laughter. If, however, you&#8217;re not too keen on them, but you&#8217;re planning a party which happens to fall around Halloween, they&#8217;re perfect!<br />
If you hire a professional clown, they&#8217;ll have plenty of games that will entertain the children. Getting everyone to come as their own version of a clown would be fun too!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/clown-birthday-party/">Clown Birthday Party</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
