      <description>Halloween is the perfect time to let your daughter hold a slumber party. Beyond the usual DVDs, you need to include some fun slumber party activities to keep everyone involved and having fun. photo credit: St0rmz One of my daughters&amp;#8217; favorites is to do pumpkin carving. Best of all, the inside of the pumpkin could [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/halloween-slumber-party-activities/"&gt;Halloween Slumber Party Activities&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Halloween_Slumber_Party_Activities.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Halloween is the perfect time to let your daughter hold a slumber party. Beyond the usual DVDs, you need to include some fun slumber party activities to keep everyone involved and having fun.</p>
<p><a title="Thanksgiving 2008" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/80742119@N00/3065671765/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3169/3065671765_690e12c6b3_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Thanksgiving 2008" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution-ShareAlike License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="St0rmz" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/80742119@N00/3065671765/" target="_blank">St0rmz</a></small></p>
<p>One of my daughters&#8217; favorites is to do pumpkin carving. Best of all, the inside of the pumpkin could be used to make a delicious pumpkin soup or pie. Deciding whether you involve the girls in the cooking will develop on their age.</p>
<p>Telling age-appropriate scary stories is also fun, and you can&#8217;t beat getting all the girls to dress up in costumes to make the event go off with a bang!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/halloween-slumber-party-activities/">Halloween Slumber Party Activities</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
