      <description>A mystery party can be confusing for young children. However, regardless of their age, if you are planning a mystery party, there are a few games that when played at a mystery party children will have an awesome time. photo credit: Margaret Anne Clarke I Spy is a classic that never goes out of style. [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/games-mystery-party-children-love/"&gt;Games At A Mystery Party Children Will Love&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Games_At_A_Mystery_Party_Children_Will_Love.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>A mystery party can be confusing for young children. However, regardless of their age, if you are planning a mystery party, there are a few games that when played at a mystery party children will have an awesome time.</p>
<p><a title="Question mark" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24350382@N07/2949435839/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3182/2949435839_a53d509915_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Question mark" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Margaret Anne Clarke" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24350382@N07/2949435839/" target="_blank">Margaret Anne Clarke</a></small></p>
<p>I Spy is a classic that never goes out of style. Remember that some games which may be old fashioned to you could be being played by the children for the very first time. If you like, you can spice I Spy up a bit by incorporating actions and singing.</p>
<p>Another game which should be played at a mystery party is Wink Murder. This game is so much fun, and can be adapted in so many ways to suit any theme you may be incorporating.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/games-mystery-party-children-love/">Games At A Mystery Party Children Will Love</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
