      <description>To introduce a bit of variety to the next birthday party you hold for your child, try to include a few outside party games. These will help the group release some of their pent-up energy, and let you prepare the party room for other games later on. A party game which my daughters love to [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/outdoor-party-games/awesome-party-games/"&gt;Awesome Outside Party Games&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Awesome_Outside_Party_Games.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>To introduce a bit of variety to the next birthday party you hold for your child, try to include a few outside party games.</p>
<p>These will help the group release some of their pent-up energy, and let you prepare the party room for other games later on.</p>
<p><small><a title="audi_insperation" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/78394307@N00/3840228857/" target="_blank"></a></small></p>
<p>A party game which my daughters love to play outside is a twist on the normal Scavenger Hunt.</p>
<p><a title="Run!" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/78394307@N00/3840228857/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3487/3840228857_c495b8ae36_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Run!" /></a></p>
<p>Instead of searching for treats, each person has to find an item which has been assigned to them. The quicker they find it, the more points they get. If they find someone else&#8217;s item, they have to tell an adult who will add bonus points to their score (but they must not hide the other child&#8217;s item in a different place!).</p>
<p>Points convert into prizes.</p>
<p><small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="audi_insperation" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/78394307@N00/3840228857/" target="_blank">audi_insperation</a></small></p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/outdoor-party-games/awesome-party-games/">Awesome Outside Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
