      <description>Slumber parties are a great time for girls to enjoy some slumber party dress up games. These can be as wide ranging as you can imagine; and it&amp;#8217;s a great idea to let the girls come up with some suggestions of what they would like to dress up as. photo credit: a_real_horrorshow_devotchka Maybe they want [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/slumber-party-dress-games/"&gt;Slumber Party Dress Up Games&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Slumber_Party_Dress_Up_Games.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Slumber parties are a great time for girls to enjoy some slumber party dress up games.</p>
<p>These can be as wide ranging as you can imagine; and it&#8217;s a great idea to let the girls come up with some suggestions of what they would like to dress up as.</p>
<p><a title="Getting Tired of Wings" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/28965400@N06/3870857859/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2492/3870857859_4777273fc6_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Getting Tired of Wings" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="a_real_horrorshow_devotchka" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/28965400@N06/3870857859/" target="_blank">a_real_horrorshow_devotchka</a></small></p>
<p>Maybe they want to be fairies or princesses; maybe they want to be glamorous actresses or French models! It&#8217;s excellent preparation to buy a few metres of cheap fabric or curtain material, so the girls can make their own costumes. Have some make-up and hair styling products and accessories handy too!</p>
<p>The girls could compete to dress up in record time; maybe the other girls could decide what the chosen girl should dress up as!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/slumber-party-dress-games/">Slumber Party Dress Up Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
