      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/?p=514</guid>
      <description>When planning a party or a play-date for girls, it’s vital that you give some thought to what group party games and birthday party activities can be included. Not only are they are a way of keeping the girls entertained, but they also assist in teaching them social skills. They’re great for you too, as [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/party-games-for-girls/party-games-for-girls/"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Party_Games_For_Girls.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>When planning a party or a play-date for girls, it’s vital that you give some thought to what <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/group-party-games" target=" " title="group party games">group party games</a> and birthday party activities can be included.</p>
<p>Not only are they are a way of keeping the girls entertained, but they also assist in teaching them social skills. They’re great for you too, as they give you a chance to focus on what else needs to be prepared for the party.</p>
<p><a title="party games for girls" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/40645538@N00/3351774095/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0pt none;" title="Party Games For Girls" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3614/3351774095_872c6ea7f0.jpg" border="0" alt="party games for girls" width="280" height="186" /></a>Making the choice of which party games to include will depend on many factors, including (a) the guests’ ages, gender and preferences, (b) the venue, (c) whether the games are indoor party games or outdoor party games, (d) when the games will be played (e.g. a slumber party will need more games than a usual party, and not all games are suitable for <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/slumber-party-games" target=" " title="slumber party games">slumber party games</a>) and (e) whether there is a theme (e.g. a mystery theme will require mystery party games, and a princess theme will require <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/princess-party-games" target=" " title="princess party games">princess party games</a>).</p>
<p>Three golden rules to remember when planning <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com" target=" " title="party games for girls">party games for girls</a> are:</p>
<ul>
<li>It’s often more straightforward (and easier on the purse) to hold the party at home</li>
<li>Girls love to be involved and challenged, so get them to suggest games that they want to play</li>
<li>Theme parties (where everyone comes in character) already stand out from the usual parties and are a great way to invent new party games by adapting the rules of traditional party games to suit the theme.</li>
</ul>
<p>Giving the girls a hand in creating the party will ensure that the party is unique and that the guests enjoy themselves and are engaged.</p>
<p>Have fun!</p>
<p><small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="../wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Pink Sherbet Photography" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/40645538@N00/3351774095/" target="_blank">Pink Sherbet Photography</a></small></p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/party-games-for-girls/party-games-for-girls/">Party Games For Girls</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
