      <description>One of the many indoor party games kids will love is Caterpillar Tag. Each of the children has to lie down on the floor. One person is the tagger, and has to tag the other players. The twist in this version of tag is that all of the players are on the floor, on their [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/indoor-party-games-kids-love/"&gt;Indoor Party Games Kids Will Love&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-Indoor_Party_Games_Kids_Will_Love.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>One of the many <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/indoor-party-games" target=" " title="indoor party games">indoor party games</a> kids will love is Caterpillar Tag.</p>
<p>Each of the children has to lie down on the floor. One person is the tagger, and has to tag the other players. The twist in this version of tag is that all of the players are on the floor, on their front, and have to move like caterpillars.</p>
<p><a title="Chinese Oak Silkmoth (Antheraea pernyi) caterpillar, final instar" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/33465428@N02/3945990180/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2576/3945990180_9fde38ae68_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Chinese Oak Silkmoth (Antheraea pernyi) caterpillar, final instar" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution-NoDerivs License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Deanster1983" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/33465428@N02/3945990180/" target="_blank">Deanster1983</a></small></p>
<p>It&#8217;s a great game to play if it&#8217;s raining outside, because it doesn&#8217;t become too boisterous. My daughters loved pretending to be caterpillars too.</p>
<p>If you want the game to be played outside, maybe the players could become butterflies and have to chase each other flapping their wings!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/indoor-party-games-kids-love/">Indoor Party Games Kids Will Love</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
