      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/?p=58</guid>
      <description>Some of the best girl birthday party activities are the ones where the girls are involved. The best way to do this is to use crafts. Little girls love making things, and to see what they have made form an integral part of the party is a real treat for them too. photo credit: upton [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via the &lt;a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/girl-birthday-party-activities/"&gt;The Best Girl Birthday Party Activities&lt;/a&gt; is a post from: &lt;a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com"&gt;Party Games For Girls&lt;/a&gt; blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/party-games-for-girls/Party_Games_For_Girls-The_Best_Girl_Birthday_Party_Activities.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Some of the best girl <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/birthday-party-activities" target=" " title="birthday party activities">birthday party activities</a> are the ones where the girls are involved.</p>
<p>The best way to do this is to use crafts. Little girls love making things, and to see what they have made form an integral part of the party is a real treat for them too.</p>
<p><a title="IMG_4501" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/50972268@N00/3960151624/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2476/3960151624_208eb596c9_m.jpg" border="0" alt="IMG_4501" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution-NoDerivs License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="upton" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/50972268@N00/3960151624/" target="_blank">upton</a></small></p>
<p>My girls love baking. One of their favorites is to bake cookies in different shapes, like animals or flowers. I usually add some food coloring to make them look extra special, and the girls adore decorating them with colored frosting and edible glitter.</p>
<p>Beautiful <em>and </em>delicious!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/girl-birthday-party-activities/">The Best Girl Birthday Party Activities</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
