      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/?p=40</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[Girls will be girls! My daughters love playing princess and having princess themed parties. This is a game that you can play with the guests or before the guests arrive (and which will help you organize the rest of the party!). It&#8217;s generically called &#8216;Princess Decorating Games&#8217;, but basically involves the girls helping to decorate [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/princess-party-games/princess-decorating-games/">Princess Decorating Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
