      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/?p=20</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[Games which involve guessing are great fun and ensure that the party goers use their brains. One of my favorite guessing party games is &#8216;Blindfolded Monkey&#8217;. For this, you will need an eye-mask (or some fabric which is sturdy enough to act as a blindfold). photo credit: Alfonso Jiménez Attach the blindfold to one of [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/group-party-games/guessing-party-games-2/">Guessing Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Games which involve guessing are great fun and ensure that the party goers use their brains.</p>
<p>One of my favorite guessing party games is &#8216;Blindfolded Monkey&#8217;. For this, you will need an eye-mask (or some fabric which is sturdy enough to act as a blindfold).</p>
<p><a title="The Monkey" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/68458516@N00/3950942119/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2669/3950942119_8903a6b6e8_m.jpg" border="0" alt="The Monkey" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution-ShareAlike License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Alfonso Jiménez" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/68458516@N00/3950942119/" target="_blank">Alfonso Jiménez</a></small></p>
<p>Attach the blindfold to one of the girls and get the other children to stand in a circle around the blindfolded girl. Each of the partygoers must now act like monkeys and walk around the blindfolded girl in the circle.</p>
<p>When the blindfolded girl says &#8216;Monkey Monkey&#8217;, the girls must stop walking and act like monkeys on the spot. The task of the blindfolded girl is to guess the identities of as many monkeys as possible.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/group-party-games/guessing-party-games-2/">Guessing Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
