      <description><![CDATA[When you have a party at home, you need to have something to keep the children occupied. That&#8217;s where home birthday party activities come in. There are sometimes so many activities to choose from that it can be quite overwhelming. However, one of my favorites (and one of the more successful) home birthday party activities [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/home-birthday-party-activities/">Home Birthday Party Activities</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>When you have a party at home, you need to have something to keep the children occupied. That&#8217;s where home <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/birthday-party-activities" target=" " title="birthday party activities">birthday party activities</a> come in.</p>
<p>There are sometimes so many activities to choose from that it can be quite overwhelming.</p>
<p>However, one of my favorites (and one of the more successful) home <a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/birthday-party-activities" target=" " title="birthday party activities">birthday party activities</a> is to play &#8216;Simon Says&#8217;.</p>
<p><a title="Tug-o-war" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/36946048@N05/3701419549/" target="_blank"><img style="border: 0pt none;" title="Home Birthday Party Activities" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2542/3701419549_1fc079fd7f_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Tug-o-war" width="240" height="212" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Reverend Barry K." href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/36946048@N05/3701419549/" target="_blank">Reverend Barry K.</a></small></p>
<p>The &#8216;Simon&#8217; part can be replaced by the name of the birthday girl, and is played in the traditional way (i.e. the child wil say &#8220;[Name] say to do&#8230;&#8221;, and everyone follows; should the birthday girl say &#8220;Do&#8230;&#8221; without saying their name first, everyone who follows these instructions loses).</p>
<p>We&#8217;ve amended the rules before to include &#8216;Speedy Simon Says&#8217;, where everything is done very quickly; this is lots of fun and one you should try.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/home-birthday-party-activities/">Home Birthday Party Activities</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/home-birthday-party-activities/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
    </item>
