      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/?p=185</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[If you&#8217;ve got girls staying over for a slumber party, it&#8217;s a great idea to include some slumber party crafts to keep them entertained. Activities where children get involved are much better than activities where children are passive (e.g. just watching a dvd). The great thing about slumber parties is that they can be longer [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/slumber-party-crafts/">Slumber Party Crafts</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
