      <description><![CDATA[Mystery Party Games are traditionally quite difficult to organize. However, this need not be the case with this idea. Either in advance of the party (to allow the girls to come in fancy-dress) or at the start of the party, give each girl the name of a character that they have to play during the [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-games/">Mystery Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p><a class="ld_link" href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/mystery-party-games" target=" " title="Mystery Party Games">Mystery Party Games</a> are traditionally quite difficult to organize. However, this need not be the case with this idea.</p>
<p>Either in advance of the party (to allow the girls to come in fancy-dress) or at the start of the party, give each girl the name of a character that they have to play during the party (e.g. variations of famous singers or actors).</p>
<p><a title="Let Me Tell You Something" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/88904268@N00/3378205556/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3614/3378205556_648a9d2ac0_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Let Me Tell You Something" /></a><br />
<small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Photo Mojo" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/88904268@N00/3378205556/" target="_blank">Photo Mojo</a></small></p>
<p>Each girl will also need their own secret which you can give them on the day or which they can make up.</p>
<p>Using their character, each girl must try to find out as many of the other girls&#8217; secrets as possible.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-games/">Mystery Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
