      <description><![CDATA[This is one of the funniest indoor icebreaker games we&#8217;ve come across. It&#8217;s one we made up (and have tested over and over again!) called Princess Witch Diva. photo credit: ~*Bomba Rosa*~ This game is a lot like scissors/papers/stones, but it&#8217;s a lot more dramatic and a great way for a new group of girls [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/indoor-icebreaker-games/">Indoor Icebreaker Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
