      <description><![CDATA[Traditionally, outdoor youth games are for youth groups and are designed to cater for larger groups of children. A game which involves everyone is a fun way of uniting the group. One game is RED ROVER RED ROVER. To play this, the group will need to be divided into equal (or near equal) groups. Each [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/outdoor-party-games/outdoor-youth-games/">Outdoor Youth Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
