      <description><![CDATA[A relatively calming game to include in your slumber party ideas is the straw-marshmallow game. It can either be played in two teams sitting opposite each other or by all girls together sitting in a circle. Everyone puts a drinking straw in their mouth and the first person sticks a marshmallow onto the end. The [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/slumber-party-ideas/">Slumber Party Ideas</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
