      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>A relatively calming game to include in your slumber party ideas is the straw-marshmallow game.</p>
<p>It can either be played in two teams sitting opposite each other or by all girls together sitting in a circle.</p>
<p>Everyone puts a drinking straw in their mouth and the first person sticks a marshmallow onto the end. The aim of the game is to pass the marshmallow around the circle (or down the line) using only the drinking straws in your mouth.</p>
<p>Ways to make this harder are for the girls to have a marshmallow in their mouth (or a mouthful!) while trying to pass the other marshmallow.</p>
<p>If the girls don&#8217;t like marshmallows (or you would like to do something healthier), maybe try passing strawberries!</p>
<p><a title="campfire marshmellow" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/23823986@N05/3853457775/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3543/3853457775_0bce6f072a_m.jpg" border="0" alt="campfire marshmellow" /></a><br />
