      <description><![CDATA[Sometimes it&#8217;s good for party games to be played outside. This idea will provide you with some really fun games for kids outside. You&#8217;ll need some chalk and some outside space. On the ground, use the chalk to mark out a grid measuring at least four square by four squares. Each square should be large [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/outdoor-party-games/games-for-kids-outside/">Games For Kids Outside</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
