      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Just because it&#8217;s raining outside, doesn&#8217;t mean you can&#8217;t enjoy some indoor picnic games!</p>
<p>A great start is to get the girls to decide what they want to eat. These can be made by each in advance or made at the venue.</p>
<p><a title="Hjertelig pizza" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/68978695@N00/3874668348/" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2497/3874668348_ae5b3bd209_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Hjertelig pizza" /></a><br />
