<p>A great way of entertaining girls where there are not many of them is to include some adults in the games. One of our favorites is the pharoah mummy! Using a bag of fabric rags, the girls will compete (either in teams or individually) to see who can mummify the adult in their team the fastest. You can switch mummies and award prizes based on speed, lengths of rags used or whatever you can think of!</p>
