      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/?p=72</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[If you&#8217;re holding a mystery party, one of the key ways to guarantee its success is to have interesting mystery party characters. You can either set these in advance or give your guests some scope to decide for themselves. Either way, it&#8217;s important that you choose a theme which has enough scope to give people [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-characters/">Mystery Party Characters</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
