      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>If you&#8217;re holding a mystery party, one of the key ways to guarantee its success is to have interesting mystery party characters.</p>
<p>You can either set these in advance or give your guests some scope to decide for themselves. Either way, it&#8217;s important that you choose a theme which has enough scope to give people lots of choice.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/15363357@N00/3689808/" title="Purple Beauty" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/3/3689808_8cb6c2372e_m.jpg" alt="Purple Beauty" border="0" /></a><br /><small><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" title="Attribution License" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" alt="Creative Commons License" border="0" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/15363357@N00/3689808/" title="Jan Tik" target="_blank">Jan Tik</a></small></p>
<p>Each of the girls will need to write down interesting facts about their character (the number of interesting facts will need to be equal to the number of other girls playing the game). These facts will then need to be distributed to the girls so that each girl has one fact about each of the other characters (i.e. if there are ten girls playing, then each girl will need one fact about each of the other nine girls).</p>
<p>The girls will then have to act in their characters to try and get the missing facts about themselves before any of the other characters do.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-characters/">Mystery Party Characters</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-characters/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
    </item>
