      <description><![CDATA[Guessing party games are lots of fun and a great ice-breaker. One of our favorite guessing party games is Wink Diva Drama Queen. This may sound similar to wink murder, but a lot less blood is spilled in this version! One of the girls is chosen as the Casting Agent, and she leaves the room. [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/guessing-party-games/">Guessing Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>Guessing party games are lots of fun and a great ice-breaker.</p>
<p>One of our favorite guessing party games is Wink Diva Drama Queen. This may sound similar to wink murder, but a lot less blood is spilled in this version!</p>
<p>One of the girls is chosen as the Casting Agent, and she leaves the room. The rest of the girls stand in a large circle, facing outwards with their eyes closed.</p>
<p>An adult walks around the circle and touches one of the girls on the shoulder. This girl is the Director, but the other girls do not know which one of them is the Director.</p>
<p>The aim of the Director is to wink at each of the other girls in the circle before the Casting Agent finds out who the Director is.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/65561583@N00/3612750852/" title="Japanese Tea Garden San Francisco" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3610/3612750852_1cbdb9f1f4_m.jpg" alt="Japanese Tea Garden San Francisco" border="0" /></a><br /><small><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" title="Attribution License" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" alt="Creative Commons License" border="0" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/65561583@N00/3612750852/" title="Donna &#038; Andrew" target="_blank">Donna &#038; Andrew</a></small></p>
<p>The girls face each other and the Casting Agent stands in the middle of the girls.</p>
<p>When winked at, each girl must act as though they are a diva drama queen, before falling to floor, sobbing and then sitting, waiting for the other girls to be winked at. It&#8217;s therefore a competition between the Director and the Casting Agent. Sooo much fun!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/guessing-party-games/">Guessing Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/indoor-party-games/guessing-party-games/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
    </item>
