      <description><![CDATA[Three great ways play a fun princess dress up game are to have the girls trying to look like (a) the best princess ever, (b) the worst princess ever or (c) a combination of both. photo credit: edenpictures It would be a great idea to have a few bags of clothes or fabric samples so [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/princess-party-games/princess-dress-up/">Princess Dress Up</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
