      <description><![CDATA[A theme that is always popular with girls is to have a tea birthday party. Although it might seem obvious that tea is needed, this is not so, as a tea birthday party is characterized by having adult-type food and drink in child-friendly (and tasty!) portions. You could even spice it up by having an [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/birthday-party-activities/tea-birthday-party/">Tea Birthday Party</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
