      <description><![CDATA[When holding a slumber party, it&#8217;s important to incorporate games and activities to ensure slumber party fun is had by all. Slumber parties are usually strictly girls only. Depending on how old the girls are, suitable movies can be watched, accompanied with treats made specially (maybe by some of the girls together during the day; [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/slumber-party-fun/">Slumber Party Fun</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
