      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>When holding a slumber party, it&#8217;s important to incorporate games and activities to ensure slumber party fun is had by all.</p>
<p>Slumber parties are usually strictly girls only. Depending on how old the girls are, suitable movies can be watched, accompanied with treats made specially (maybe by some of the girls together during the day; or maybe by each girl bringing something different for everyone else to share).</p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24458886@N07/3184302709/" title="Slumber party cupcakes" target="_blank"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3326/3184302709_a978662b84_m.jpg" alt="Slumber party cupcakes" border="0" /></a><br /><small><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" title="Attribution License" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" alt="Creative Commons License" border="0" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24458886@N07/3184302709/" title="wishuponacupcake" target="_blank">wishuponacupcake</a></small></p>
<p>It&#8217;s always fun to let the girls go crazy with some make-up and hair styles (appropriately overseen as necessary). Fashion shows and catwalks, whether they be of teddys or the girls themselves,<br />
is another way for the girls to have a blast!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/slumber-party-fun/">Slumber Party Fun</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/slumber-party-games/slumber-party-fun/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
    </item>
