      <description><![CDATA[Generally, survivor party games are more suitable for boys. However, it really depends on the preferences of the girls at the party and the type of survivor party games that are played. If the girls don&#8217;t mind getting dirty and running about, some team games that pitch them against the other side are a great [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/outdoor-party-games/survivor-party-games-2/">Survivor Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
