      <description><![CDATA[An essential component of holding a mystery party are mystery party scripts. Girls simply love role playing and getting into character, so the script could either be a full length script or short enough to give the girls an idea of what their character is like. This will then allow them to be as imaginative [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-scripts/">Mystery Party Scripts</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
