      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>An essential component of holding a mystery party are mystery party scripts.</p>
<p>Girls simply love role playing and getting into character, so the script could either be a full length script or short enough to give the girls an idea of what their character is like. This will then allow them to be as imaginative as possible; making it fun for everyone!</p>
<p>A box of old clothes and fabrics is a great way to let the girls accessorize their new characters, and it&#8217;s completely up to you what the actual mystery is. Sometimes it&#8217;s better to focus on the girls creating their characters, rather than worry about coming up with a mystery. If you&#8217;re stuck, perhaps one of the girls is really a princess or has been selected to go to ballet or rap school!</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/mystery-party-games/mystery-party-scripts/">Mystery Party Scripts</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
