      <description><![CDATA[Pool party games can be enjoyed by all sorts of girls. One excellent game to play is to have a mermaid swimming competition. You&#8217;ll need at least two girls (mermaids) and an appropriate number of adult supervisors. photo credit: Tom@HK Each girl will be given the chance to swim as much like a mermaid as [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/outdoor-party-games/pool-party-games/">Pool Party Games</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
