      <description><![CDATA[Girls and boys tend to like playing different types of games at parties. When you&#8217;re planning a party and you know there&#8217;ll be a mix of boys and girls, a treasure hunt game is a great way to get everyone involved and having fun. A fairly easy and inexpensive way to ensure each stop on [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.PartyGamesForGirls.com/group-party-games/treasure-hunt-game/">Treasure Hunt Game</a> is a post from: <a href="http://www.partygamesforgirls.com">Party Games For Girls</a> blog where you can get great ideas for children's party games and the latest news on party games for girls</p>
